@article{15279371220220201,
 abstract  = "• An implementation strategy design method of physical entities for manufacturing systems DT is proposed to analyze the implementation strategy of the DT-application from the top level, which makes the implementation strategy more scientific and takes full advantages of DT to solve specific application problems of physical entities. • Physical entity for DT deployment scheme design method is explored, which integrates the design domain of axiomatic design with the design domain of physical entity. • The operability and effectiveness of the proposed physical entity for DT deployment scheme design method is validated through CNCMT cutting tool life prediction. Digital Twin (DT) technology, as one of the top ten strategic technology trends for 2020, has received widespread attentions and gradually being used in manufacturing system. However, for the implementation strategy of these applications, most of the current researches are focused on the digital aspect (data processing, algorithm ",
